439
00:31:18,650 --> 00:31:20,625
Hei, tunggu sebentar.

440
00:31:21,044 --> 00:31:23,262
Oalah, jancuk.

441
00:31:23,263 --> 00:31:27,223
Tunggu,
apa yang kamu lakukan di dalam sana?

442
00:31:27,224 --> 00:31:30,635
- Bajigur!
